computer interaction (HCI).<br /><br /><i><u>Clarifications</u></i>:<br/><i>Clarification 1:</i> Technologies may include augmented reality (AR), virtual reality (VR) and others.</span></td></tr></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="1" style="border-collapse: collapse" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bordercolor="#000000"><tr><td width="25%" align="center" Valign="top"><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: Arial">SC.6.ET.1.2</span></td><td width="75%"><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: Arial">Identify technology skills needed in the workplace.</span></td></tr></table><br/><div id="ShowBOKLabels" runat="server"><table align="center" width="100%" border="1" BorderColor="Black" style="border-collapse: collapse" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr style="height: 23.1pt"><td width="100%" valign="middle" style="background: #CCCCCC"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; color: Black; font-family: Arial"><asp:Label Font-Bold="true" ID="Label2" runat="server">Standard</asp:Label><asp:Label Font-Bold="true" ID="Label3" runat="server"> 2: </asp:Label><asp:Label Font-Bold="true" ID="Label5" runat="server">Identify Artificial Intelligence (AI) and its applications.</asp:Label><br /><br /><div><asp:Label ID="Label6" Font-Italic="true" runat="server"></asp:Label></div></span></td></tr></table></div><table align="center" width="100%" border="1" style="border-collapse: collapse" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bordercolor="black"><tr><td bordercolor="black" width="25%" align="center" bgcolor="#CCCCCC"><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: Arial"><b>BENCHMARK CODE</b></span></td><td bordercolor="black" width="75%" align="center" bgcolor="#CCCCCC"><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: Arial"><b>BENCHMARK</b></span></td></tr></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="1" style="border-collapse: collapse" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bordercolor="#000000"><tr><td width="25%" align="center" Valign="top"><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-famil