.1.6</span></td><td width="75%"><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: Arial">Explore the innovation of computer components.</span></td></tr></table><br/><div id="ShowBOKLabels" runat="server"><table align="center" width="100%" border="1" BorderColor="Black" style="border-collapse: collapse" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr style="height: 23.1pt"><td width="100%" valign="middle" style="background: #CCCCCC"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; color: Black; font-family: Arial"><asp:Label Font-Bold="true" ID="Label2" runat="server">Standard</asp:Label><asp:Label Font-Bold="true" ID="Label3" runat="server"> 2: </asp:Label><asp:Label Font-Bold="true" ID="Label5" runat="server">Recognize the regulations surrounding the use of information.</asp:Label><br /><br /><div><asp:Label ID="Label6" Font-Italic="true" runat="server"></asp:Label></div></span></td></tr></table></div><table align="center" width="100%" border="1" style="border-collapse: collapse" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bordercolor="black"><tr><td bordercolor="black" width="25%" align="center" bgcolor="#CCCCCC"><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: Arial"><b>BENCHMARK CODE</b></span></td><td bordercolor="black" width="75%" align="center" bgcolor="#CCCCCC"><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: Arial"><b>BENCHMARK</b></span></td></tr></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="1" style="border-collapse: collapse" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bordercolor="#000000"><tr><td width="25%" align="center" Valign="top"><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: Arial">SC.7.TI.2.1</span></td><td width="75%"><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: Arial">Describe legal and ethical behaviors when using information and technology and describe the consequences of misuse.</span></td></tr></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="1" style="border-collapse: collapse" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bordercolor="#000000"><tr><td width="25%" align="center" Valign="top"><span style="font-size: 